-- MGIC Selects Moody's Analytics Economist Zandi to Join Board of Directors
-- Peter Eichenbaum
-- 2010-07-22T16:54:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/mgic-selects-moody-s-analytics-economist-zandi-to-join-board-of-directors.html

          
          
             MGIC Investment Corp., the biggest
U.S. mortgage guarantor, said  Mark Zandi , chief economist at
Moody’s Analytics, has joined the insurer’s board of directors.  
 Zandi received his doctorate at the University of
Pennsylvania, Milwaukee-based MGIC said today in a statement
distributed by PR Newswire.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Peter Eichenbaum in New York at 
 peichenbaum@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        